<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a2Feb1938"><font color="red">2 February 1938</font> <i>NLHW</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Harriet Weaver):  I gave Mr Joyce the O&apos;Reilly clan paper which he was glad to have &hellip; object was to avoid any application to the Irish Times Office in Dublin &hellip; he is reluctant to ask Mr Curran in Dublin to do this kind of thing for him in connection with his book as he is to ask yourself &hellip; </div>
